Package: mtr-ng
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Modern My Traceroute with real-time network path visualization
 MTR-NG is a modern implementation of the My Traceroute (MTR) network diagnostic
 tool. It combines the functionality of traceroute and ping in a single tool with
 beautiful Unicode sparklines, real-time visualization, jitter analysis, and
 advanced column customization. Perfect for network troubleshooting and monitoring.
 .
 Key features:
  * Real-time network path discovery and monitoring
  * RTT statistics with min/max/average/EMA calculations
  * Packet loss detection and jitter analysis
  * Unicode sparklines for RTT history visualization
  * Color-coded metrics and customizable columns
  * Interactive UI with keyboard controls
  * Report mode for automation and scripting 